##List in HTML

    Lists are used to represent real life list data.
    
      a) unordered lists
        
        <ul>
        
        <li> Apple </li>
        
        <li> Mango </li>
    
        </ul>
    
      b) ordered lists
    
        <ol>
        
        <li> Apple </li>
    
        <li> Mango </li>
    
        </ol>



### Tables in HTML

      Tables are used to represent real life table data.
      
      <tr> used to display table row 
      
      <td> used to display table data
      
      <th> used to display table header
      
      







